Class GenericDialect

java.lang.Object
org.hibernate.dialect.Dialect
org.hibernate.annotations.processing.GenericDialect
All Implemented Interfaces:
FunctionContributor, TypeContributor, ConversionContext
public class GenericDialect extends Dialect
A generic dialect for ANSI-like SQL. Used by default in the HQL Query Validator.
